    <h3 class="muted">OUR GOAL</h3>

    <p>All organizations committed to aid projects should strive to keep their data open and transparent. Open Aid Register's goal is to assist non-profits and NGOs in making this happen by helping them publish their data in the standard known as IATI (the International Aid Transparency Initiative).</p>
    <p>By publishing data in this IATI common data standard, organizations can be sure that their aid information can be shared, understood, and used by donors, other NGOs helping in similar sectors or locations, those recipients of aid throughout the world, and the general public.</p>

