        <p class="blockquoto first">It is an extremely effective tool for NGOs to publish IATI data. We\'ve found the platform\'s interface easy to navigate and intuitive to use. Partnering with the Open Aid Register is a quick and reliable way for NGOs to contribute to the aid effectiveness movement by becoming IATI compliant.</p>
